[
  {
    "title": "Day X：福茂的迷宫",
    "category": "festival",
    "date": "2026-05-12",
    "imageUrl": "/filmtest/images/1778736544718-pq4bwk.png",
    "summary": "第79届戛纳电影节于2026年5月12日拉开帷幕，第五年来到戛纳，却是第一年以记者的身份故地重游...",
    "content": "<figure></figure><figure><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size: 13px;\">作为每年初夏的压轴盛事，南法的戛纳电影节如约而至。连续五年奔赴欧洲各大影展后，似乎已经难以容忍任何一次缺席。每一次到场，都恨不得将所有电影尽收囊中。只可惜，影展从来都伴随着无法避免的取舍，也只能不断压制那份过于旺盛的好奇心，以及无尽蔓延的「贪」。</span><br></figure>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">相比往年，今年的戛纳格外清凉。海风吹得人直打哆嗦，哪怕阳光照在身上，也远不如一件卫衣来得踏实。</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">影展整体看似仍在有条不紊地运转，但今年从一开始，便出现了不少错位且不那么顺滑的体验。抵达戛纳的当天早上，我将行李安置在预订好的民宿后，便前往证件中心领取媒体证。由于同行的媒体朋友尚未就位，为了省去他们再跑一趟的麻烦，我也打算顺手帮他们一并领取。</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">按照官方规定，电影节也曾在 Instagram 上发布动态强调：证件可以由他人代领，只需出示相关身份证件与领取邮件即可。然而真正到了柜台，工作人员却要求必须提供每个人的代取信。等我亮出官方发布的说明，对方又当场否认该说法。最终，经过一番交涉，他们还是同意了代领。想到往年也曾遭遇过类似的管理混乱，只能苦笑。</font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"/filmtest/images/1778736263992-atmlze.jpg\" alt=\"bfa58341cf4cc3fbde82a23514df48.JPG\" style=\"font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;媒体证</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">近几年，戛纳电影节通常会在正式开幕前的那个下午，以「Cannes Classics」单元的一部特选修复版影片为影展预热。比如往年曾放映过雅克·里维特《疯狂的爱情》的 4K 修复版，阿贝尔·冈斯《拿破仑（第一部分）》以及卓别林的《淘金记》等。</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">今年则由全新 4K 修复版《潘神的迷宫》拉开本届影展的序幕。然而在这场放映入场时，身边一些朋友却遇到了荒唐又可笑的状况。官方排片手册上标注的开场时间是下午 14:30，但他们在距离开场还有约 15 分钟时，就被拦在场外，不被允许入场。</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">按照惯例，这类放映前通常会有导演、导演子女，或修复团队代表上台发言，并与福茂进行互动。今年吉尔莫·德尔·托罗本人出席，因此影片本就不太可能准时开场，大约会有十来分钟的延迟。</font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<figure><img src=\"/filmtest/images/1778736302688-6mq4gb.png\" alt=\"0d61e5fcb4205c7dc45e8e72726a01e0.png\"><figcaption style=\"text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:6px\">《潘神的迷宫》映前</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">也正因如此，过了一阵子后，安保人员又突然开始放人入场。可更离谱的情况随即出现：有几位观众在安保扫描影票后被拦下，工作人员进行了第二次扫码，随后又突然表示票已被使用，因此不予入场。</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">如今听到这类事情，已经很难惊讶，只剩苦笑。毕竟过去两年，类似的管理失误也并不少见。</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">本届戛纳电影节的开幕片是《电动维纳斯》。影片的故事发生在二十世纪初的巴黎。曾经红极一时的画家安托万·巴莱斯特罗深信，妻子伊雷娜的死亡源于自己的过错，因此再也无法重拾画笔，也令画廊老板阿曼德陷入绝望。某个夜晚，为了寻求宽恕，喝醉的安托万试图通过灵媒与伊雷娜取得联系。然而他并不知道，与自己对话的其实并非亡妻，而是苏珊娜——一个身份卑微的街头艺人。她对来世一无所知，只是为了偷取食物，误打误撞溜进了算命者的马车。</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\">这里不妨借用影评人<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\">/</span>记者<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"> Bob Chow </span>的短评作为引子：</font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><img src=\"/filmtest/images/1778713003294-fa3p6d.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_3816.jpg\" style=\"font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">接下来将会定时更新每天短评和综述。</span></font></p>",
